  <h1 class="gem-c-title__text gem-c-title__text--long">
    EU Commission publishes new announcement on no deal preparations
  </h1>
</div>

  </div>
  
  <div class="govuk-grid-column-two-thirds">
    
  <p class="gem-c-lead-paragraph ">
    The EU Commission made their fifth announcement about its preparations in case the UK leaves the EU without a deal.
  </p>

  </div>
</div>

